'''Deltron spice wine''' was a type of [[Spice/Legends|spiced]] [[Wine/Legends|wine]] from [[Deltron/Legends|Deltron]]. It was fermented by a portable [[microwave]] machine and then served instantly.<ref name="marvel24">[[Star Wars (1977) 24|''Star Wars'' (1977) 24]]</ref>

Aboard [[Pleasure cruiser|Captain Quasar's pleasure cruiser]], [[Augustus Tryll]] offered a glass to [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]. Unfortunately, the signals emitted by the microwave machine attracted the attention of [[Merson pirates/Legends|Merson slavers]].<ref name="marvel24" />

[[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] fell victim to the wine's [[Alcohol/Legends|potency]] while attempting to con [[Lemo]] and [[Sanda]] on [[Arcan IV]] - after a pitcher or two too many, he inadvertently let slip his companion [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca's]] true identity.<ref name="marvel79">[[Star Wars (1977) 79|''Star Wars'' (1977) 79]]</ref>

It was also used as an ingredient in [[shaak pot roast]] served in [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="Dining">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/dexdiner/index.html|text=Dining at Dex's|int=Dining at Dex's}}</ref>

The [[mutant]] [[Terrorist/Legends|terrorist]] [[Zeta Magnus]] enjoyed eating the raw flesh of his victims with spice wine and a side of [[Arkanian diamond]]s.<ref name="SkyeWalkers: A Clone Wars Story">''[[SkyeWalkers: A Clone Wars Story]]''</ref>

